{"tid":1027591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】任正非自爆曾患抑鬱  多次想自殺","createTime":"2019-02-19T01:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T04:59:30.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fac13174b62573d1bdc938631318ce48544106bf","tid":1027591,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:55:37.000Z","msg":"孟晚舟去年底遭加拿大逮捕後，中國電訊龍頭華為董事長任正非曾為女兒多次發聲，但鮮有談及自身經歷。任正非近日與SONY行政總裁吉田憲一郎訪談時，就透露自了自創業經歷。<br />\n<br />\n任正非表示，自己44歲創業時壓力巨大，生存條件很差，完全不明白市場經濟為何物，剛從軍隊出來，認為賺別人的錢，是欺騙行為。他說：「40多歲創業是因為人生換了一次軌道，中國大裁軍，把我們部隊裁掉，然後我們就要走向市場經濟。從軍隊轉業的我，不熟悉市場經濟，活不下去，就要找一條活路。被裁軍以後，命運是很難的，我是親身體會的。當時是如何生存下來的問題。」<br />\n<br />\n他坦言創業時沒有錢，「我們家夫妻總共領了3000元人民幣轉業費，但是註冊一個公司需要2萬元人民幣，就需要去集資。所以，成立公司時我一分錢都沒有了，初創時，我自己的工資是每月500元人民幣，需要養活全家人。我早期的目標，是要生存下來。」<br />\n<br />\n「經過幾年的發展，開始走入快車道。越快，矛盾越多，各種問題交集，完全力不從心，精神幾近崩潰。」任正非說，「2000年前，我曾是憂鬱症（抑鬱症）患者，多次想自殺。直到2006年，服務員們請我吃飯，我們坐在大廳，有很多內蒙村莊的農民姑娘在唱歌，我請她們來唱歌，一首歌3美元。我看到她們那麼興奮、樂觀，這麼熱愛生活，貧困的農民都想活下來，為甚麼我不想活下來？那一天，我流了很多眼淚，從此我再也沒有想過要自殺。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190219/59275859\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190219%2F59275859&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=144041ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190219%2F59275859&h=bcc9e875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190219/59275859</a>"},{"pid":"537a2ffb7699f94834c8bdb11d29e91c6aba4e7e","tid":1027591,"uid":13115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:57:43.000Z","msg":"WFC?"},{"pid":"f2bc4cf21573cb57f0a5be3c1617d384a425fee2","tid":1027591,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"係死就快撚d"},{"pid":"8bd938f5502c18df524295874bd972c4c3cf8ce5","tid":1027591,"uid":155095,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1996050/org/b3f61b5a738429b2b49e09cfcc363ab2.jpg/wZ8aFZJu53l5L3tthlplcc3y3u3R66Tb6ohN_OqITfw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1996050%2Forg%2Fb3f61b5a738429b2b49e09cfcc363ab2.jpg%2FwZ8aFZJu53l5L3tthlplcc3y3u3R66Tb6ohN_OqITfw&h=7fba0947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2018/10/20181022-HUAMING-HONGKONG-01-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F20181022-HUAMING-HONGKONG-01-600x400.jpg&h=fe13761a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic1.dwnews.net/20181023/15402734285bceb514049a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic1.dwnews.net%2F20181023%2F15402734285bceb514049a2.jpg&h=a89a19d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca31bffbfebc892cc8392f48a32a798f412fd472","tid":1027591,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:00:39.000Z","msg":"你還有黨呀"},{"pid":"9a4bb47cf93f2fd41fb287f1058d3edfb9787b01","tid":1027591,"uid":128271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:01:06.000Z","msg":"你同個女單野再拆唔掂 <br />\n你應該好快被自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bf2d539f2dc64656123aef124fc6c4e40369e7","tid":1027591,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:14:00.000Z","msg":"預告緊自己點死?<br />\n<br />\n咁唔出奇嘅，好多黨員都有鋪被抑鬱癮"},{"pid":"d4a739e46b53aa05544ae3fab43d398c8cfdfec1","tid":1027591,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:15:04.000Z","msg":"我以為佢係為個女抑鬱,日日幻想佢點樣比加拿大獄卒輪"},{"pid":"5c3bc1c36c24f3ee4d02a7b038fe2790209c6d08","tid":1027591,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"討好歐美左膠公關手段"},{"pid":"d762a22469fee56597b66059aede3